                    <p><img class="img-fluid" alt="Macquarie " src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/logo_macquarie.svg' width="240"></p>
                    <p>This bank used microservices to modernize its IT environment.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/success-stories/macquarie" class="btn btn-link">See how</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="middleware" class="col-12 collapse">
        <div class="bg-gray-200 border-top border-bottom border-gray-400 pt-2 pb-4 mb-2">
            <p class="text-right">
                <a class="btn btn-close" tabindex="0"><img src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/icon_close-button.svg' alt='Close' class='img-fluid' /></a>
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-center mb-0">Middleware</h2>
            <div class="row justify-content-around mx-1">
                <hr class="col-md-10 my-4">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Topic</p>
                    <h4>Understanding middleware</h4>
                    <p>Middleware is any software between the kernel and user applications that provides services to apps outside of what’s offered by the operating system.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/topics/middleware" class="btn btn-link">Read more</a></p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Articles</p>
                    <nav class="nav flex-column">
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/middleware/what-is-middleware">What is middleware?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/middleware/why-choose-red-hat-middleware">Why choose Red Hat for middleware?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/mobile">Understanding enterprise mobile app dev</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/middleware/what-is-ide">What is an IDE?</a>

                    </nav>
                </div>
                <hr class="col-md-10 mt-4 mb-6">
                <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
                    <p><img class="img-fluid" alt="Schiphol Airport" src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/logo_schiphol-airport.svg' width="250"></p>
                    <p>Middleware helps the Dutch airport provide seamless journeys to customers.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/success-stories/amsterdam-airport-schiphol" class="btn btn-link">See how</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="security" class="col-12 collapse">
        <div class="bg-gray-200 border-top border-bottom border-gray-400 pt-2 pb-4 mb-2">
            <p class="text-right">
                <a class="btn btn-close" tabindex="0"><img src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/icon_close-button.svg' alt='Close' class='img-fluid' /></a>
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-center mb-0">Security</h2>
            <div class="row justify-content-around mx-1">
                <hr class="col-md-10 my-4">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Topic</p>
                    <h4>Understanding security</h4>
                    <p>IT security protects the integrity of information technologies like computer systems, networks, and data from attack, damage, or unauthorized access.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/topics/security" class="btn btn-link">Read more</a></p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Articles</p>
                    <nav class="nav flex-column">
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/technologies/guide/it-security">Why choose Red Hat for continuous IT security?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/security/what-is-hybrid-cloud-security">What is hybrid cloud security?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/security/container-security">What is container security? </a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/security/api-security">What is API security? </a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/devops/what-is-devsecops">What is DevSecOps? </a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/security/what-is-malware">What is malware?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/security/what-is-cve">What is CVE?</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <hr class="col-md-10 mt-4 mb-6">
                <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
                    <p><img class="img-fluid" alt="Banco Galicia" src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/logo_banco-galicia.svg' width="200"></p>
                    <p>The Argentine bank improved security with open source solutions.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/success-stories/banco-galicia" class="btn btn-link">See how</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="virtualization" class="col-12 collapse">
        <div class="bg-gray-200 border-top border-bottom border-gray-400 pt-2 pb-4 mb-2">
            <p class="text-right">
                <a class="btn btn-close" tabindex="0"><img src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/icon_close-button.svg' alt='Close' class='img-fluid' /></a>
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-center mb-0">Virtualization</h2>
            <div class="row justify-content-around mx-1">
                <hr class="col-md-10 my-4">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Topic</p>
                    <h4>Understanding virtualization</h4>
                    <p>Virtualization makes a single physical machine act like multiple—saving you the cost of more servers and workstations.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/topics/virtualization" class="btn btn-link">Read more</a></p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                    <p class="font-size-16 text-uppercase font-weight-light">Articles</p>
                    <nav class="nav flex-column">
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/what-is-virtualization">What is virtualization?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/what-is-virtualization-management">What is virtualization management?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/what-is-KVM">What is KVM?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/why-migrate-your-virtual-infrastructure-to-red-hat">Why migrate your virtual infrastructure to Red Hat?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/kvm-vs-vmware-comparison">KVM vs. VMware</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/cloud-computing/cloud-vs-virtualization">Cloud vs. virtualization</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/what-is-nfv">What is NFV?</a>
                        <a class="nav-link pl-0" href="/en/topics/virtualization/what-is-a-virtual-machine">What is a virtual machine?</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <hr class="col-md-10 mt-4 mb-6">
                <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
                    <p><img class="img-fluid" alt="Intermountain Healthcare" src='https://www.redhat.com/cms/managed-files/logo_intermountain-healthcare.svg' width="270"></p>
                    <p>Virtualization trimmed deployment times from weeks to hours for this provider.</p>
                    <p><a href="/en/success-stories/intermountain-healthcare" class="btn btn-link">See how</a></p>
